## ECharts Common Configurations

### Bar Chart
```javascript
{
  xAxis: { type: 'category', data: categories },
  yAxis: { type: 'value' },
  series: [{
    type: 'bar',
    data: values,
    itemStyle: { color: '#5470c6' }
  }]
}
""" ;
